{"tid":1508053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831民陣！901機場！902三罷！","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:51:34.000Z","uid":52609,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"b539eede481c9eb368dafe93af5386d0db176b9a","tid":1508053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:48:50.000Z","msg":"831民陣！901機場！902三罷！<br />\n<br />\n我要贏，要贏就要攻擊春袋！"},{"pid":"f6908b6173510dc86c36432ca109cb39d0393158","tid":1508053,"uid":33930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=0656eb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=6f56be9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=98565359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"f89968514345ef6f6e6b7a67ea35e1bfac2bd441","tid":1508053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULgKfym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULgKfym.jpg&h=b3959687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFGKfym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFGKfym.jpg&h=e81ab576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gb79rE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGb79rE1.png&h=7eb064fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e037bca3c62811210d378e78fb4390cfee60b62","tid":1508053,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"【九月機場月】九月一日開始，逢星期六日，塞爆機場交通！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n握緊春袋，港共要害！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔸行動名稱：【九月機場月】<br />\n🔸行動日子：九月逢星期六日（9月1、7、8、14、15、21、22、28、29日）<br />\n🔸開始時間：準時1pm到達機場附近<br />\n🔸結束時間：視乎情況完結/轉場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔹目標人數：每次十萬人（請立即大大力做文宣，不要停留在連登/tg同溫層）<br />\n🔹每次行動目標：癱瘓機場交通，令當日大部分香港出發的航班延誤或取消。<br />\n🔹終極目標：捉緊要害，迫使政府回應五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔶具體做法：<br />\n只阻塞進入機場的交通，不需要進入機場室內，盡量避免法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n1. 前往方法：首選 駕車&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;巴士/的士&gt;機鐵<br />\n2. 參與人數足夠情況✅：如成功令大部分航班取消，當日目標已達成，大家可自行決定離去與否。如時間尚早，可暫留在東涌或青衣以應付突發情況，或可現場討論轉戰市區。<br />\n3. 參與人數不足情況❎：避免813做法，不主動攔擋遊客，人多自然會塞到。有共識某時間內（例如三小時內，1pm-4pm）仍未有交通癱瘓跡象，請現場群眾判斷會否轉場市區。<br />\n<br />\n‼️小總結：準時1PM開始，夠人塞到取消航班，目標達成，可去東涌stand by/轉場市區/返屋企。如果共識時間內仍未癱瘓交通，轉場市區。‼️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔶注意事項/守則：<br />\n1. 準時的重要性！！準時1PM一齊去先會塞到！<br />\n2. 不進入機場室內，不舉牌，不被捕，不捉鬼<br />\n3. 小心散水流言<br />\n4. BE WATER<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔶人數是重點，人人也是文宣組<br />\n1. 時間無多，請立即開始製作不同文宣圖！<br />\n2. 不要只在連登/tg圍爐宣傳<br />\n2. 各社區街站小隊請派傳單/連儂牆宣傳九月機場月活動<br />\n3. 繁忙時段在地鐵/巴士airdrop<br />\n4. 請在Facebook/Instagram/whatsapp群組瘋狂宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔶相關Tg group：<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=74b82978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a> (<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=74b82978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>)<br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=dd2b4212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上只屬事前建議，<br />\n實際情況以現場決定為準！<br />\n握緊春袋，港共要害！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"22cc6d9bfa7f4523ee7848c649dd391d9c43624d","tid":1508053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"831民陣！901機場！902三罷！"},{"pid":"3fb49c853b4d8768ff51a07eec1ab3fc0fac51b8","tid":1508053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"831民陣！901機場！902三罷！"},{"pid":"af6a97e7df16c12d8ebd50592b6dc0e54d26b90a","tid":1508053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"831民陣！901機場！902三罷！"},{"pid":"2673d7bbcad22a5179f627fdf3f27394d73900ae","tid":1508053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"831民陣！901機場！902三罷！"},{"pid":"b1ee159e989cbcd64e9a089115a25f0bb5b062ef","tid":1508053,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"141fabb57cf823d0d959ca88f8c679159d691f6b","tid":1508053,"uid":70227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"902三罷齊齊機場見"},{"pid":"aa7915c76e8fd14bd159f93da14dea1794060cfb","tid":1508053,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4T4vVxL.j